###
### The Digi-Clone expands his territory:
###	-Infinite duration
###	-No more break range
###	-No swap cooldown
###
### For example, you can put it anywhere on the map and use it as a TP or watch how many rounds it can last in an arena while you're outside.
###
### Cancel it by reloading the map (Fast Travel).
###
### NOTE: SSpyR already did something similar with his God Clone. You can use both, just put mine after in load order.
###

